title: Abbys Ultimate Dance Competition S02E12 FINALE
description:
Episode: 12
Meet Abby's Newest Ultimate Dancer

Original Airdate: November 19, 2013 It's finally time to choose this year's Ultimate Dancer. The finalists are so close they can taste it and they'll do anything to win the $100,000 and a scholarship to the Joffrey Ballet School in New York. Everything is on the line and every move they make counts. May the best dancer win!
